title: Beyond the Horror: Asylum Episode 6
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I didn't get notification again! I'm so sad I missed y'all :(

Me pretending chat is still live:
•Arden was both, he was a Nazi doctor.
•I love Adina Porter, and Roanoke. Even episode 6, lol y'all definitely hated on Murder House more, it has Vivian.
TBH I'm not sure how to feel about the fact that we won't get the title of future season right away. it might be an interesting move to hype up the fan base but it also kinda annoys me already.
Sarah paulson and Naomi Grossman retweeted me before. Was epic
Hey willing do the wigi with u and Casey.
